<h2>Mercenary</h2>

<p>No Mercenary really survives Uber Tristram so many @@@D2Smite@@@rs who run that often don’t use mercenaries. However, for the Resistancest of the game you can either choose a Defensive (@@@D2HolyFreeze@@@) or Offensive (@@@D2Might@@@) Act 2 Nightmare Mercenary here depending on if you want even more slow and safety, or want more Damage.</p>

<ul>
<li>Weapon: Eth @@@D2Pride@@@, Eth @@@D2BreathOfTheDying@@@</li>
<li>Body Armor: Eth @@@D2Fortitude@@@</li>
<li>Helm: Ral’d Eth @@@D2AndarielsVisage@@@</li>
</ul>

